01:06:50,640 --> 01:06:52,676
Oh, creep.

493
01:07:10,120 --> 01:07:13,795
Eli, come here, help me up.
She's gonna hurt herself, hold her up.

494
01:07:20,680 --> 01:07:23,240
Pull her legs.

495
01:07:28,520 --> 01:07:29,953
I saw that mister.

496
01:07:34,480 --> 01:07:37,119
I know you're there, asshole.

497
01:07:39,160 --> 01:07:41,469
Listen perv, don't make me call the...

