I can't cover for you anymore.

506
01:10:09,080 --> 01:10:10,957
Is Hannah with you?

507
01:10:13,680 --> 01:10:17,798
Meet me at the convent, okay.
- Sandy, just come home. Sheriff Mitchell stopped by the house.

508
01:10:17,960 --> 01:10:20,190
Please meet me there.

509
01:10:30,640 --> 01:10:32,631
I thought we're on a hurry.

510
01:11:00,440 --> 01:11:03,432
May I help?
- Sorry to bother you...

511
01:11:03,600 --> 01:11:07,070
I'm Sandy Channing and this is my friend...
- Jake Mitchell.

512
01:11:07,240 --> 01:11:10,232
The quarterback?
- Yes ma'am.

513
01:11:10,400 --> 01:11:16,077
Father Michael and I, we listen
to all the games on the Hi-Fi.

514
01:11:16,240 --> 01:11:20,028
I'm Sister Dolores. Please come in.

515
01:11:23,120 --> 01:11:26,590
I'm sorry sister, I know it's late.
- What can I do for you?

516
01:11:26,760 --> 01:11:29,399
We're here because of Angela Smith.

517
01:11:30,520 --> 01:11:35,071
How do you know her?
- I used to know her when I was little.

518
01:11:35,240 --> 01:11:38,630
Of course.
- Sister, Sandy is just concerned...

519
01:11:38,800 --> 01:11:43,191
Is Angela her?
- Oh, I wish she was...

520
01:11:43,360 --> 01:11:47,148
but it's just not practical,
I'm sure you understand.

521
01:11:47,320 --> 01:11:51,233
Do you know where she might be?
- At St. Mary's hospital.

522
01:11:51,400 --> 01:11:55,439
They're quite wonderful there.
- Is she hurt?

523
