Oh, I'm sorry.
I assumed you knew.

525
01:12:07,280 --> 01:12:08,838
A coma?

526
01:12:10,520 --> 01:12:15,719
Thank you for your time.
- Well, I could show you her room.

527
01:12:19,880 --> 01:12:23,634
I've kept her room just as she's left it.

528
01:12:23,800 --> 01:12:29,397
Her doctors say that her condition
is permanent but well one hopes...

529
01:12:30,640 --> 01:12:35,111
Oh well, the girls' floor...
- Mr. Mitchell can wait down here on the boys' floor.

530
01:12:35,280 --> 01:12:40,752
Can he come with me?
- I'll be fine. I'll stay here on the boys' floor.

531
01:12:42,120 --> 01:12:43,633
Please, come in.
Come in. Come in.

532
01:12:50,760 --> 01:12:56,073
Girls, girls, game time is over.
Ride along.

533
01:12:56,240 --> 01:12:59,994
Say your prayers.
I'll be there and I'll tuck you in a moment.

534
