A little rhyme I teach the children.

535
01:13:05,840 --> 01:13:09,435
It helps to keep the nightmares at bay.

536
01:13:18,080 --> 01:13:23,074
Do you believe in the devil, Mr. Mitchell?
- No, not really.

537
