- No, sweetheart. She just needs some help.

623
01:24:15,280 --> 01:24:19,432
No, no. You're not going anywhere, alright. Sit down.
- Let go.

624
01:24:20,880 --> 01:24:23,440
You don't understand, please.

625
01:24:28,680 --> 01:24:33,754
It's gonna be okay, honey.
- You'll get back to normal in no time.

626
01:24:33,920 --> 01:24:36,593
We're gonna take very good
care of you, Ms. Channing.

627
01:24:36,760 --> 01:24:39,399
Sandy, I'm here. I'm right here.
- Step aside.

628
01:24:43,520 --> 01:24:45,988
For Christ's sake. Somebody hold him down.
- Sandy, tell me what to do?

629
01:24:46,160 --> 01:24:50,597
Kill the ghost or seal your fate.
- What is she saying?

630
01:24:50,760 --> 01:24:53,877
Kill her?
- Kill her.

631
01:24:54,040 --> 01:24:55,393
You can't go any further.

632
01:24:57,400 --> 01:25:01,393
I'll do it, Sandy. I'll do it.

633
01:25:28,360 --> 01:25:30,032
Midnight.

634
01:25:32,440 --> 01:25:37,036
Stop. Let me go.
Let me go.

635
01:25:40,520 --> 01:25:45,674
Eli? Where is Eli?
- What is she saying?

636
01:25:45,840 --> 01:25:49,037
Who's Eli, honey?
- Is Eli one of her friends?

637
01:25:50,680 --> 01:25:56,755
Sandy doesn't have any friends.
- Go to sleep, honey. We'll be here when you wake up.

638
01:25:58,440 --> 01:25:59,953
Angela Smith.

639
01:26:03,480 --> 01:26:07,473
That's strange.
Angela Smith is a patient here.

640
01:26:16,600 --> 01:26:19,068
I thought we could play the game?

641
01:26:19,240 --> 01:26:23,028
Who's playing?
- Just us.

642
01:26:36,480 --> 01:26:39,313
I'm sorry about last time.

643
01:26:41,200 --> 01:26:43,589
It's getting late. We should play.

644
01:26:52,320 --> 01:26:57,189
Maybe we shouldn't play.
- No, I want to play.

645
01:26:57,360 --> 01:26:59,510
Wait. Who's the ghost?

646
01:27:01,320 --> 01:27:02,673
