647
01:27:04,000 --> 01:27:09,393
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven
release the one ignored by heaven.

648
01:27:11,760 --> 01:27:13,671
Run.

649
01:27:17,480 --> 01:27:19,550
Help me.

650
01:27:33,680 --> 01:27:35,432
Midnight.

651
01:27:53,560 --> 01:27:56,438
Look at that shit.

652
01:28:13,360 --> 01:28:15,237
Who did this?

653
01:31:16,360 --> 01:31:18,590
