654
01:31:24,640 --> 01:31:27,438
but I also know what you've done.

655
01:33:45,760 --> 01:33:48,194
You wanna play a game?

656
01:33:50,880 --> 01:33:56,352
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven
release the one ignored by heaven.

657
01:33:56,520 --> 01:33:59,637
eight, nine, ten, now run and hide
or join her at the devil's side.

658
01:33:59,800 --> 01:34:04,590
I remember you. I remember everything.
- Eleven comes, the clock will chime
forgotten souls erased by time.

659
01:34:04,760 --> 01:34:08,799
I'm so sorry.
